values: that's what valentines day is going to be called in the future, just V-day. People already call it that, but there'll be greeting cards in the future that just say V-DAY. I'm telling you.

I'm 22 years old and I still don't know how to file my goddamned tax returns!!! I was just about to say "they should teach you how to do this fucking shit in school", when i realized...they actually do. 
This year I'm gonna really take the initiative and have my mom do them.
......while I'm watching her to see how it's done. Halfheartedly. I'll probably be watching the tv instead.

I NEED THIS MONEY! I wanna get the eee laptop by Asus in Blush pink.

Holy shit! I haven't made a post in 93 weeks!

I've been gone for a little while now, but the other day I was like what the fuck! i should go back into that old livejoural again, i had a lot of friends there".  
.....so i did, I deleted THREE YEARS worth of entries, and now I'm starting fresh. 

I'm happy to be back again, bitches.

LOVE, jenna
